{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so my mother was born in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they were married forever and forever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember that, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, from day one, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't leave the farm because I wanted to leave the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was picked up in 1943 in the night of October 1st, 1943.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- about-- later on, maybe 20 minutes later, we went to this guy, Henry's farm, picked him up too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was Danish-- Danish people on the truck who evidently were part of the SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I never forget and-- and I'll tell you something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been thinking about that so much in the-- especially in the last year or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been-- I says-- what happened was one of the SS men, the Danish SS men says to me and Henry and the-- they didn't-- they couldn't pull into the yard with the truck, you know. so they there were standing, you know, it was like an enclosed, you know, the typical farms were sort of like surrounded with an opening, right?",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they couldn't pull in because they figured they couldn't turn them around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he says, you and you, get him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go over and get this guy, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we go, we run over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the guy, we get him out of bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, what are you, crazy?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm going to-- I ain't going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he jumps out a window and takes off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I look at Henry and we were so brainwashed that time with the Germans that we went back to the goddamned truck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many years I've said to myself, my god, I would have-- I wouldn't have had a happy death in the gas chambers, I'd be thinking about I could have run away and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
